Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.42,0:16:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷了還能這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.93,0:17:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炮擊型 想射沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算哈雷路亞不在！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大氣層中對方機動性占憂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你有Veda撐腰…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞．艾迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是 變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.26,0:17:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我們共同完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是變革者的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭正在擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.74,0:18:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 公主陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.12,0:18:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能讓大家聽到我們的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我們唱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.67,0:18:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然微不足道 但也不能放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖不忍心射殺同類
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但必須履行使命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也有不能退讓之處
