Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.75,0:18:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和Nadleeh當初不同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.05,0:18:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此番登場乃有意為之
