Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.40,0:19:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對同類也要下手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.91,0:19:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布林．斯塔比利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提耶利亞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你囂張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞斯 有MS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:19:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:20:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是來護航的嗎
